                <div class='quote'>
                <h3>"[…] because of this box, the samples I got, I like how it performs - I would buy this filament.
                […] and that’s the point of this. To try out a filament to see if you want to buy a larger roll of it… and I’m going to buy a larger roll of it because this is freaking cool."</h3>
                <h3>- Joel from <a href='https://the3dprintingnerd.com'>3D Printing Nerd</a> on the virtues of our Maker Box subscriptions</h3>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class='recently-featured'>
        <div class='recently-featured-container'>
            <div class='maker-box-title'>
                <h1>Recently Featured Filaments</h1>
            </div>
            <span class="title_divider"></span>
            <div class='recently-featured-logos'>
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_1 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_2 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_3 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_4 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_5 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_6 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_7 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_8 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_9 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_10 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_11 | img_url: '200x' }}">
                <img class="recently-featured-logo" src="{{section.settings.recently_featured_filaments_12 | img_url: '200x' }}">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class='mailing-list'>
        <div class='mailing-list-content'>
            <h3>Stay updated with Maker Box</h3>
            <form action="https://www.getdrip.com/forms/577145636/submissions" method="post" data-drip-embedded-form="577145636" id="drip-ef-577145636">
                <div>
                    <input type="email" id="drip-email" name="fields[email]" value="" placeholder="Email Address">
                </div>
 
                <div style="display: none;" aria-hidden="true">
                  <label for="website">Website</label><br>
                  <input type="text" id="website" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="false" value="">
                </div>
                
                <div>
                  <input class='sign-up-button' type="submit" value="Sign Up" data-drip-attribute="sign-up-button">
                </div>
              </form>
  {% include 'maker-social-media' %}
        </div>
          

    </div>
</section>

